information: The company HÄUSSERMANN STAUDEN+GEHÖLZE GMBH HÄUSSERMANN UND MARKUS HÄUSSERMANN, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1929, which operates in the Cereals and grains industry. It also operates in the Vegetables, edible roots and tubers, Bedding plants, bulbs and seeds, Indoor and greenhouse plants, floristry, and Nurseries industries. It is based in Möglingen, Germany.
